      "date": "2024-01-11 22:48:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe following sessions will be run for build 101276 patch 1\n\nEnforced:\n- review-ldiskfs-dne on el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n- review-ldiskfs-dne-arm on el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and el8.8-aarch64/ldiskfs clients\n- custom on el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and el9.3-x86_64/ldiskfs clients\n- custom on el8.9-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs clients\n\nMaloo Test Queue: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_queue?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=101276&commit=Apply+Filter\nMaloo Results: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/related?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=101276#redirect",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "79d38bbdcb5108ebb254c0b24dc1ac3708a8c817",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 147,
